window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I was a nobody until my diving team conquered the first two dungeons in the Path of Progression. And now? I’m famous. Throughout Aspatria, everyone knows my name, and they’re all talking about just how powerful our team can become.</p> <p>My enemies are taking notice too. After defeating the fabled Slayer in the second dungeon, I know someone is waiting to take their revenge on me. I need to watch my back as we set our sights on the next two dungeons. I also need to make sure my team of ass-kicking beauties continues to develop too, especially when a girl from my past shows interest in joining us.</p> <p>It’s not going to be easy, but if I wanted easy, I would have just stayed home.</p> <p><b>Join me now for the next book in the Dungeon Heroes saga!</b></p>"; 
